  <div id="bottomscript_0_DivScript">
   <script type="text/javascript">
    var DosGoogleSearchHelper = {};

        DosGoogleSearchHelper.cseSingstat = "006524738387304832746:dcudfh9pcou";
        DosGoogleSearchHelper.cseGov = "006524738387304832746:yqrxzhlskt8";

        DosGoogleSearchHelper.invokeSearch = function (searchKey, isGov) {
            if (isGov) {
                window.open("http://www.google.com/cse?q=" + searchKey + "&cx=" + this.cseGov, "_blank");
            }
            else {
                window.open("http://www.google.com/cse?q=" + searchKey + "&cx=" + this.cseSingstat, "_blank");
            }
        };

        DosGoogleSearchHelper.keywordDesktop = function () {
            return jQuery("#siteSearchDesktop").val();
        };

        DosGoogleSearchHelper.keywordMobile = function () {
            return jQuery("#siteSearchMobile").val();
        };

        DosGoogleSearchHelper.searchLocation = function () {
            return jQuery("#selectedLocation").val();
        }

        DosGoogleSearchHelper.keyCode = function (evt){
            return (evt.charCode) ? evt.charCode : ((evt.which) ? evt.which : evt.keyCode);
        };

        DosGoogleSearchHelper.invokeDesktopSearch = function () {
            var searchKey = DosGoogleSearchHelper.keywordDesktop();
            var selectedLocation = DosGoogleSearchHelper.searchLocation();

            if(searchKey !== ''){
                if (selectedLocation === "all") {
                    DosGoogleSearchHelper.invokeSearch(searchKey, true);
                }
                else {
                    DosGoogleSearchHelper.invokeSearch(searchKey, false);
                }
            }
        }

        DosGoogleSearchHelper.invokeMobileSearch = function () {
            var searchKey = DosGoogleSearchHelper.keywordMobile();
            if (searchKey !== '') {
                DosGoogleSearchHelper.invokeSearch(searchKey, false);
            }
        }

        jQuery(document).ready(function () {
            jQuery("#searchMobile").on("click", function () {
                DosGoogleSearchHelper.invokeMobileSearch();
            });

            jQuery("#siteSearchMobile").keyup(function (evt) {
                if (DosGoogleSearchHelper.keyCode(evt) == 13) {
                    DosGoogleSearchHelper.invokeMobileSearch();
                    e.preventDefault();
                }
            });

            jQuery("#searchDesktop").on("click", function () {
                DosGoogleSearchHelper.invokeDesktopSearch();
            });

            jQuery("#siteSearchDesktop").keyup(function (evt) {
                if (DosGoogleSearchHelper.keyCode(evt) == 13) {
                    DosGoogleSearchHelper.invokeDesktopSearch();
                    e.preventDefault();
                }
            });
        });
   </script>
